// SYNTAX TEST "Packages/todo/todo.sublime-syntax"
todo
====
1 syntax coloring
2 folding
3 move finished groups to bottom
+ text blocks
+ expand page headings (==)
+ expand section headings (--)
+ prioritised lists (1)

shortcuts
~~~~~~~~~
- ctrl + alt + .?-=

commands
--------
> mark as [todo, doing, question, done]
- clear done
- run formatter
- make page heading (====)
- make section heading (----)
- merge into one (heading: item)
- split into many
- move [group, page] [up, down]
- promote / demote

notes format
'''
    title
    ==

    heading
    --
    item
    - sub item (todo format)
'''

todo format
'''
    heading
    -- (optional)
    - to do item
    + done item
    ? unsure whether to do or not
    > work in progress
    1 prioritised item
'''
